rows.label: tlk42400013_07_msg0002

merchant ship doing business on its own without
permission from the guild, mo.

rows.label: tlk42400013_07_msg0003

If they do business without following the guild's
rules, the market will be thrown into chaos, mo.

rows.label: tlk42400013_07_msg0004
rows.name: If that happens, our business will be ruined, mo!

rows.label: tlk42400013_07_msg0005
rows.name:
Could you perhaps board that merchant ship
and send them to hell for me, mo?!
